      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 2,
      "message": "Pam.. just so I can be sure I am understanding how this works.. Does this mean the decision will be a permit unless there is at least one deny?  Meaning a response of \"indeterminate\" would still return a permit? What exactly is the difference between this and deny-overrides? just for my own understanding...",
